Package org.ejvm.frontend Description

Contains frontends for the usage of the eJVM Development Kit as well as the execution of compiled eJVM programs.

The following frontends are provided:

  • eJVMCompiler: Command line utility for invocation of the eJVM compiler.
  • eJVMDump: Command line utility for the inspection of compiled eJVM programs.
  • eJVMExecutor: Command line utility for the execution of compiled eJVM programs.

Since:
1.0
